---
title: Beef Shawarma Lettuce Wraps with Tomato & Garlicky White Sauce
description: Looking for the flavors of a shawarma-stuffed pita and the cool, refreshing crunch of a lettuce wrap? look no further! You’ll fill crisp baby lettuce leaves with shawarma-spiced beef, juicy diced tomato, tangy quick-pickled shallots. Don’t forget to finish the dish with a drizzle of garlicky white sauce for the full shawarma effect!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6772d1d3555c15a993e5701f-90c6c178.jpeg
